    "media:imagetext": "FOR A MORE\nENJOYABLE FLIGHT\nIn this flight packet, you will find many\nthings of interest. For example, there is a\nmap for your use in locatng your position\nfrom the air ... a complete booklet that\nanswers practically all the questions you\nmay have about your Flagship and how it\nflies... postcards... and much more. This\npacket is for you, so why not take it with\nyou as a souvenir of your flight.\nHowever, there may be something you\nwant but don't see. If so, just push the call\nbutton and your stewardess will be at your\nside in a moment to fill your wish. If you\nwant to send a telegram, just ask her-she'll\ngive you the blanks and see that it's sent at\nthe next airport. She will also help you plan\nyour continuing or return trip with the aid\nof the In-Flight Reservations form in this\npacket. In fact, she will be a constant\nsource of assistance throughout the flight.\nOn the ground, as in the air, you'll find\nAMeriCan AIRLINES ready, and willing, to\nserve you whetner its plannig a vacation\nin Mexico, or arranging to have a rental\ncar awaiting your arrival at the airport. All\nyou have to do is ask at any Reservations\nor Ticket Office. You will find AMERICAN\nAIRLInes a complete travel service with\nbut a single purpose - to make your trip\nmore enjoyable.\nAMERICAN AIRLINES\nFLAGSHIP\nINFORMATION\nAIRLINES\nAmerica's Leading Airline\nAA Form T106F\nLitho in U.S.A.",
